== 事件 ==

* 10月 － [[华纳通讯|华纳通讯]]从[[诺兰·布什内尔|诺兰·布什内尔]]受伤以2800万美元收购[[雅达利|雅达利]]。布什内尔依然担任[[主席|主席]]<ref name="icwhen">{{cite web| author=Thomas, Donald A. Jr| year=2005| title=–1976–| url=http://www.icwhen.com/book/the_1970s/1976.shtml| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080212154559/http://www.icwhen.com/book/the_1970s/1976.shtml| archivedate=2008-02-12| format=shtml| work=ICWhen.com| accessdate=18 February 2006| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
* 电子游戏销量超过350万，当年电子游戏产业收益达2.42亿美元<ref>[http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=wNohAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DaAFAAAAIBAJ&pg=5716,245390 TV Games Probed] {{Wayback|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=wNohAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DaAFAAAAIBAJ&pg=5716,245390 |date=20211003040127 }}, Reading Eagle (December 21, 1976)</ref>。

== 知名发行 ==

* 1月 － [[世嘉|世嘉]]发行《[[重量级冠军|重量级冠军]]》，是首款[[格斗游戏|肉搏]]游戏<ref name="tao">Spencer, Spanner, [http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/the-tao-of-beat-em-ups-article?page=1 The Tao of Beat-'em-ups] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/the-tao-of-beat-em-ups-article?page=1 |date=20200205133945 }}, ''EuroGamer,'' Feb 6 2008, Accessed Feb 23, 2009</ref><ref name="ashcraft">Ashcraft, Brian, (2008) ''Arcade Mania! The Turbo-Charged World of Japan's Game Centers'', (Kodansha International), p. 94</ref><ref>Nadia Oxford, [http://www.1up.com/features/20-years-street-fighter 20 Years of Street Fighter] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20121206043053/http://www.1up.com/features/20-years-street-fighter |date=2012-12-06 }}, [[1UP.com|1UP.com]], 12/11/2007</ref>。游戏用模拟挥拳的[[游戏控制器|控制器]]<ref name="tao" />。
* 2月 － 世嘉发行《[[Road_Race|Road Race]]》，这款[[竞速游戏|竞速游戏]]引入[[伪3D|伪3D]]、向前卷轴和[[第三人称游戏|第三人称]]图形<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arcade-history.com/?n=road-race&page=detail&id=14493 |title=Road Race arcade video game by SEGA Enterprises (1976)<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2015-01-23 |archive-date=2020-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828152643/https://www.arcade-history.com/?n=road-race&page=detail&id=14493 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="road_race">{{KLOV game|12733|Road Race}}</ref>。
* 4月 － [[Taito|Taito]]发行《[[Speed_Race_Twin|Speed Race Twin]]》，作为《Speed Race》的续作，游戏可以双人彩色[[多监视器|双屏]]对战<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arcade-history.com/?n=speed-race-twin&page=detail&id=19477 |title=Speed Race Twin arcade video game by Taito (1976)<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2015-01-23 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128025618/https://www.arcade-history.com/?n=speed-race-twin&page=detail&id=19477 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{KLOV game|9711|Speed Race Twin}}</ref>。
* 4月 － 雅达利发行[[街机游戏|街机游戏]]《[[Breakout|Breakout]]》（样机由[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]共同创办人[[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史蒂夫·乔布斯]]和[[史蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克|史蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克]]设计）<ref name="icwhen" />。它引发了各种[[打砖块|打砖块式游戏]]。
* 8月 － 世嘉发行《[[Man_T.T.|Man T.T.]]》（又名“Moto-Cross”）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arcade-history.com/?n=man-t.t.&page=detail&id=26084 |title=Ryu ga Gotoku Zero: Chikai no Basho sony playstation 3 game by SEGA (2016)<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2015-01-23 |archive-date=2020-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828151156/https://www.arcade-history.com/?n=man-t.t.&page=detail&id=26084 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，这是早期[[摩托车|摩托车]]竞速游戏，和《Road Race》类似采用伪3D、向前卷轴、第三人称视角<ref name="road_race" /><ref name="Moto">{{KLOV game|12812|Moto-Cross}}</ref>。游戏还引入[[触觉反馈|触觉反馈]]，让手把在[[碰撞检测|碰撞]]时震动<ref>Mark J. P. Wolf (2008), ''The video game explosion: a history from PONG to PlayStation and beyond'', p. 39, [[ABC-CLIO|ABC-CLIO]], ISBN 0-313-33868-X</ref>。[[Gremlin_Industries|Sega-Gremlin]]以“Fonz”重做品牌<ref name="Fonz">{{KLOV game|id=12812|name=Fonz}}</ref>。
* 8月 － [[快捷半導體|快捷半導體]]发行了[[Channel_F|Video Entertainment System]]（后来叫VES或Channel F），是一款使用[[微处理器|微处理器]]和[[ROM卡带|卡带]]的电子游戏机<ref name="channelf">{{cite web| title=Fairchild Video Entertainment System/Channel F| url=http://www.classicgaming.com/museum/channelf/| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520113518/http://www.classicgaming.com/museum/channelf/| archivedate=2011-05-20| work=[http://www.classicgaming.com/ ClassicGaming.com]| accessdate=18 February 2006| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
* 10月 － 雅达利发行第一人称视角竞速游戏《[[Night_Driver|Night Driver]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arcade-history.com/?n=night-driver-upright-model&page=detail&id=26054 |title=Night Driver arcade video game by Atari, Inc. (1976)<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2015-01-23 |archive-date=2020-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828143956/https://www.arcade-history.com/?n=night-driver-upright-model&page=detail&id=26054 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* [[Exidy|Exidy]]发行了电影《[[Death_Race_2000|Death Race 2000]]》改编的[[竞速游戏|竞速游戏]]《[[Death_Race_(游戏)|Death Race]]》。游戏暴力元素引发公众抗议，在许多地区被禁止<ref name="deathrace">{{cite web| author=Gonzalez, Lauren| title=When Two Tribes Go to War: A History of Video Game Controversy / The Major Offenders| url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6090892/p-2.html| work=[http://www.gamespot.com/ GameSpot]| accessdate=18 February 2006| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5QPSTXWbi?url=http://www.gamespot.com/| archivedate=2007-07-17| deadurl=no}}</ref>。
* [[Coleco|Coleco]]发行《[[乓|乓]]》的仿制游戏机[[Coleco_Telstar|Telstar]]，游戏机采用[[通用仪器|通用仪器]]的AY-3-8500[[集成电路|微芯片]]<ref name="telstar">{{cite web| author=Winter, David| year=2006| title=Coleco Telstar| url=http://www.pong-story.com/coleco_telstar.htm| work=[http://www.pong-story.com/ PONG-Story]| accessdate=18 February 2006| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060302100623/http://www.pong-story.com/coleco_telstar.htm| archivedate=2006-03-02| deadurl=no}}</ref>。
* [[Radofin|Radofin]]在欧洲发行[[1292_Advanced_Programmable_Video_System|1292 Advanced Programmable Video System]]游戏机<ref name="1292apvs">{{cite web| author=Hansen, Dale| year=2002| title=1292 Advanced Programmable Video System FAQ version APVS.01| url=http://www.digitpress.com/faq/1292faq.txt| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100513024714/http://www.digitpress.com/faq/1292faq.txt| archivedate=2010-05-13| format=text| accessdate=18 February 2006| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
* [[唐·伍兹|唐·伍兹]]在[[斯坦福大学人工智能实验室|斯坦福大学人工智能实验室]]工作时，发现并扩展了[[威尔·克劳瑟|威尔·克劳瑟]]的《[[Colossal_Cave_Adventure|Adventure]]》。下半年[[James_Gillogly|James Gillogly]]用[[C语言|C语言]]将伍兹的这款用[[Fortran|Fortran]]编写的[[视觉小说|视觉小说]]移植到[[Unix|Unix]]电脑上<ref name="adventure">{{cite web| author=Adams, Rick| title=A history of 'Adventure'| url=http://www.rickadams.org/adventure/a_history.html| work=The Colossal Cave Adventure page| accessdate=17 February 2006| archive-date=2011-05-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110517000635/http://www.rickadams.org/adventure/a_history.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

